configSettings.title: Forecast
configSettings.description: Perform contact scheduling off of most recently published contact schedule

configSettings.title: ForecastMin
configSettings.description: Minimum amount of time to allow from current time to forecast start

configSettings.title: CshPeriod
configSettings.description: Amount of time a new contact schedule should span

configSettings.title: CshLockout
configSettings.description: Period of time from current time to lock out scheduling new contacts

configSettings.title: TpPeriod
configSettings.description: Amount of time from current time to generate tasks in Pleniter

configSettings.title: VisPeriod
configSettings.description: Amount of time from current time + contact lockout period by which visibilities are retrieved

configSettings.title: StatusPeriod
configSettings.description: Number of hours from current time to retrieve unavailabilities

configSettings.title: MaxAttempts
configSettings.description: Max number of times the Harness can re-attempt contact scheduling after rejection
